data.name: Abdomen
data.value: The front of a vertebrate body from the breastbone to the pelvis.

data.name: Calve
data.value: The back portion of the lower leg.

data.name: Chest
data.value: The trunk of the body from the neck to the abdomen.

data.name: Forearm
data.value: The part of the arm between the elbow and the wrist.

data.name: Hip
data.value: The projecting part of each side of the body formed by the side of the pelvis and the upper part of the femur.

data.name: LowerBack
data.value: The rear part of the body, extending from the middle to the lower end of the spine.

data.name: Neck
data.value: The part of the body that connects the head and the trunk.

data.name: Shoulder
data.value: The part of each side of the body at the top of the trunk, extending from each side of the base of the neck to the region where the arm articulates with the trunk.

data.name: Thigh
data.value: The part of the lower limbs between the hip and the knee.

data.name: UpperArm
data.value: The upper limb of the body extending from the shoulder to the elbow.

data.name: UpperBack
data.value: The rear part of the body, extending from the base of the neck to the middle of the spine.
